WEBVTT

00:00:29.492 --> 00:00:32.601
Velika nejednakost
u zemljama u razvoju

00:00:32.601 --> 00:00:36.026
čini teškim da se uvidi,
na primer,

00:00:36.026 --> 00:00:38.590
da po pitanju prevoza

00:00:38.590 --> 00:00:40.520
napredan grad nije onaj

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:42.542
gde čak i siromašni voze kola,

00:00:42.542 --> 00:00:44.565
nego onaj gde čak i bogati

00:00:44.565 --> 00:00:46.789
koriste javni prevoz.

00:00:46.789 --> 00:00:50.355
Ili bicikle.
Na primer, u Amsterdamu

00:00:50.355 --> 00:00:52.385
više od 30 procenata
stanovništva

00:00:52.385 --> 00:00:53.920
koristi bicikl

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:55.818
uprkos činjenici
da Holandija ima

00:00:55.818 --> 00:00:59.801
veći prihod po glavi stanovnika
od SAD.

00:00:59.801 --> 00:01:03.658
Postoji sukob
u zemljama u razvoju